Despite the rapid growth of digital banking, many customers struggle to fully adopt and engage with banking services. A significant number of users abandon the onboarding process, fail to activate key digital services such as UPI and mobile banking, or remain inactive after account creation. Existing banking solutions largely rely on reactive customer support and generic notifications, resulting in low personalization and limited customer engagement.
Banks face challenges in understanding individual customer needs, providing timely guidance, and encouraging continuous usage of digital banking platforms. This leads to reduced customer retention, lower digital transaction volumes, and missed opportunities for financial inclusion and product adoption.
There is a need for an intelligent, proactive, and personalized solution that can autonomously guide customers throughout their banking journey, improve digital adoption, increase engagement, and help banks build stronger customer relationships at scale using Agentic AI.
